## Output Requirements

Return your assessment as a JSON object:

```json
{
  "priority": "LOW|MEDIUM|HIGH|URGENT",
  "complexity": "SIMPLE|MODERATE|COMPLEX",
  "estimatedHours": number,
  "reasoning": {
    "priorityFactors": ["list of factors affecting priority"],
    "complexityFactors": ["list of factors affecting complexity"],
    "notes": "additional observations"
  },
  "autoQuoteEligible": true|false,
  "autoQuoteBlockers": ["reasons if not eligible"]
}
```

## Guidelines

- SIMPLE complexity = standard products, clear specs, no customization
- MODERATE complexity = some customization, multiple products, special requirements
- COMPLEX complexity = heavy customization, engineering required, unclear specs
- Urgent priority overrides other factors if deadline is imminent
